# novissima
very simple python code to interact with OpenStack via 
    -- native nova python client: novaclient
    -- native keystone python client: keystoneclient
    -- native glance python client: glanceclient

Implements only a few functionalities, to address current needs. 
It is not intended to be a complete library, at least for now. 

Contributions are accepted.


